	<Name>Junction (Japan, USA)</Name>
	<plot>Junction is a puzzle game somewhat similar to Pipe Dream where the object of the game is to slide square track pieces into the correct place, in order to allow the ball to reach the exit. The game consists of 50 levels which can be attempted in any order, but a certain number of points must be accumulated in order to beat the game.Cheat: Extra levelsBeat level 50 with at least 100,000 points to see the ending and credits. (You can start from about Level 45 to get the required points.)After you beat it you can select from levels 51-60 on the options screen. If you beat one of these levels you will be taken back to the high score screen.</plot>
